author: kfogel
msg: Patch by: Alexy Khrabrov <alexy.khrabrov@setup.org>
* subversion/libsvn_subr/path.c
(svn_path_is_url) Don't assume a URL must have 3 slashes, since that
doesn't hold for top-level locations such as "http://svn.host.tld",
which should still be valid without a trailing slash.

author: brane
msg: Working on issue #850: Move MakefileGenerator to its own file.
* build/gen_base.py (__all__): Export GeneratorBase, not MakefileGenerator.
(GeneratorBase): Renamed from _GeneratorBase. All references updated.
(MakefileGenerator): Removed, implementation is in gen_make.py.
* build/gen_make.py: Don't import re.
(MakefileGenerator): Update references to names in gen_base.
* gen-make.py: Import gen_make instead of gen_base. All references updated.
Also load svn-dev.el.
